Ammi

Ammi is a brand of fillers based on hyaluronic acid created by Beautiful Korea Co., Ltd. The series represented by four products including Ammi Aqua, Ammi Crystal,  Ammi Hydro, and Ammi Diamond. Ammi fillers are manufactured using unique patented technology Nano-Mesh Cross-Linking, demonstrate high efficiency if applied for correction of age-related skin changes and restoration of loss volumes on face, and represent the biocompatible and safe cosmetological items.

B-esta

B-esta is a brand of body fillers based on hyaluronic acid by BNC Global Co. The series is represented by two products B-esta 10 Body Filler and B-esta 50 Body Filler. Subcutaneous injection of the fillers promotes volumerization of the desired areas. Since the products have an optimal viscosity, it enables the specialist to easily re-shape the selected area, providing the most natural looking silhouette. The effect of fillers lasts up to two years, and the results of injections become visible immediately after treatment.

Beads Max

Beads Max is a brand of fillers developed on hyaluronic acid (HA) by Maxcore Global Co., Ltd. This series contains five products: Beads Max Fine, Beads Max Mid, Beads Max High, Beads Max Body Classic-H, and Beads Max Body Classic-S, differentiated by the degree of HA polymerization, and suitable for resolution of certain issues. Using these fillers, the one can correct the wrinkles with different degree of manifestation, remodel the face and body shape as well as restore the loss volumes.

Bellast

Bellast is a series of fillers established by Dongkook Pharma Co., Ltd. For the first time, the company applied the double polymerization technology for the manufacturing of the brand products. As a result, they obtained three fillers: Bellast Soft L, Bellast Ultra L, and Bellast Ultra Plus. Using them, it is possible to correct wrinkles with moderate and high degree of manifestation as well as deep folds on the forehead and in glabella area, significantly diminish the nasolabial folds, remodel the face shape and conduct lips augmentation.

Bentpla

Bentpla is a brand of recovery and anti-inflammatory gels from the South Korean company Tai Guk Pharm Co. Ltd. The brand is represented by Bentpla gel, an external application-only recovery product for the skin. The active components of the product result in the complex improvement of bruised and irritated skin. 
Tai Guk Pharm has been committed to the production of outstanding pharmaceutical products, and their products are a result of years of research and development, combining years of knowledge with effective ingredients to nourish, heal, and restore the skin, and remove any discomfort.

Berаcaine

Berаcaine is a brand from the South Korean manufacturer Firson Co. Ltd. Berаcaine is an aerosol spray product for the skin designed and developed to help alleviate pain during and after injectable aesthetic procedures and make the process more comfortable both for doctors and patients. The brand has created an effective product based on the analgesic and antiseptic properties of lidocaine to simplify aesthetic procedures and other minor surgeries and speed up the recovery process.
